      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "text": "NON-FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS: 3Min\n\n1} LATENCY: \n100ms - 200ms\n\n2} SCALABILITY:\n1B recruiter like personas across global\n5 booking per day\n5B booking per day\nbooking QPS = 5B/86400 = 50K QPS\n\n3} Highly available\n\n4} Strong consistent\n\n5} Failure Tolerant\n\n\n",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "QgVwJIfOQpOLaIhYCF7m4",
      "originalText": "NON-FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS: 3Min\n\n1} LATENCY: \n100ms - 200ms\n\n2} SCALABILITY:\n1B recruiter like personas across global\n5 booking per day\n5B booking per day\nbooking QPS = 5B/86400 = 50K QPS\n\n3} Highly available\n\n4} Strong consistent\n\n5} Failure Tolerant\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
