      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "text": "FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS: 2Min\n\nIn-SCOPE Recruiter: \n\n1. Sign-up\n2. Integrate Corporate Cal (Microsoft,\nGmail) [P0]\n3. Generate Security URL, to send to \ncandidate. [P0]\n4. Updated Calendar\n\n2. In-SCOPE Candidates:\n1. Availability for next for week with Security URL\n2. Book a session:  [P0]\n- Recruiter's calendar updated in real time\n- Corporate Calendar gets updated\n- Recruiter Email notification \n- Candidate email notification\n ",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "RrmrBYiIxZ0gldIz2RuZg",
      "originalText": "FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS: 2Min\n\nIn-SCOPE Recruiter: \n\n1. Sign-up\n2. Integrate Corporate Cal (Microsoft,\nGmail) [P0]\n3. Generate Security URL, to send to \ncandidate. [P0]\n4. Updated Calendar\n\n2. In-SCOPE Candidates:\n1. Availability for next for week with Security URL\n2. Book a session:  [P0]\n- Recruiter's calendar updated in real time\n- Corporate Calendar gets updated\n- Recruiter Email notification \n- Candidate email notification\n ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
