      "text": "Table\n\n3] Calendar\n   - calendar_id:\n   - owner_recruiter_id: \n   - calendar_type: \n\n\n4] URL Table\n   - url_id\n   - candidate_email\n   - celndar_id:\n   - owner_recruiter_id: \n   - url_string\n   - start_time\n   - end_time\n\n\nhttps://calendly.com/abcdefg --> \n\nhttp://microsoft/calendar(recruiter, startdate-enddate)",
